title: BREAKING: Senate Makes Decision On Rex Tillerson For SecState…

Republicans were on the warpath today. Democrats to slow down the nominees. They were not successful. One of the nominees who Democrats most wanted to defeat was Rex Tillerson. Tillerson had been painted as too close to Russia by Democrats, with no governmental experience. Republican pointed to his broad international business experience.
